The definition of brunch heaven at @greenwoods_tearoom 😍🍳 Did you know that all dishes are served all day? 😴 Perfect for late sleepers! Variations include the eggs benedict (€12,95), "The Keizers Veggie" (€12,95) with eggs on halloumi, crispy roast potatoes, avocado, Portobello mushrooms and tomato and the "Banana Bread Tumble" (€10,95) with toasted banana bread, white chocolate mascarpone, fresh blueberries, strawberries, toasted almonds and coconut flakes 👌 Too good!

#amazinglytasty feast of #asian tastes @happyhappyjoyjoyams, a #streetfood restaurant with great food and staff that takes making you #happy very seriously. Sticky rice in lotus leave, indonesian, spicy pineapple, apple and cucumber salad, steamed bun with crispy chicken and yuzu mayo, #killer pork and shrimp dumplings, pad thai, #delicious steamed bun with duck and wasabi mayo and banana fritters with yuzu sorbet and toasted coconut chips. Will be back for sure! #amsterdamfood #amsterdamfoodie #asianfusion #sharejoy #introverteats
